models

user:(use devise用户)
  avatar
  email
  password(8位，必须是字母和数字的混合,前端设个强度指示的检查,jiecheng(2/24))
  nick_name
  real_name(姓名不用分开jiecheng(2/24))
  id_card_number
  abstract
  has_many :followings
  id_card_check(3 pics)
  cell
user增加身份证图片、正面、反面、手持身份证。

account:（某个用户的账户，余额、角色、评论、私信）
  user_id
  balance
  role: investing fund
  has_many :comments
  has_many :messages
  has_many :check
  level

##fund:（发标，标的名字、操盘手、额度、到期时间、收益、收益率、状态、投标s）
```ruby
  name:string
  user_id:references
  amount:decimal{12,2}
  colleciton_deadline:datetime
  earning:decimal{12,2}
  earning_rate:decimal{6,4}
  state:string in {on, off}
  has_many: invests
  has_many: comments
  private_item:boolean
  minimum:decimal{12,2}
  invest_starting_date:datetime
  invest_ending_date:datetime
  industry??
```
homs
子账户用户名、密码、
